@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@missingUserId = 000000000000000000000000

# 用法:
# 1. 「黄金路径」按顺序从上到下点,靠 REST Client 的具名请求变量(如 {{demoCreate.response.body.$._id}})
#    自动把上一步返回的 _id 传给下一步,不用手动复制粘贴。
# 2. 「二/三、边界与错误场景 · 400/404」内部每条互相独立,demo 讲健壮性时按需挑着点。
# 3. 「四、边界与错误场景 · 409」内部有顺序依赖(seed A/B → 两条 409 测试 → 两条清理),
#    要按顺序整组跑,不能像 400/404 那样挑单条点,否则 seed 请求没跑过,后面几条会因为
#    引用不到 seedUserA/B 的返回值而失败。
# 4. Postman 版见 users.postman_collection.json,分组和顺序与本文件一致。
# 5. 下面出现的固定 id(如 000000000000000000000000)是故意选的、保证不会撞上真实数据的
#    占位 id,不需要你替换成数据库里的真实 _id——真正需要真实 _id 的地方都已经用具名请求
#    变量自动传递了,不需要手动改。

### ============================================================
### 一、黄金路径 · 完整生命周期演示(推荐 demo 主线)
### ============================================================

### 1. List users - 创建前的基线
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

### 2. Create user - 成功创建
# Expected: 201,响应体带 MongoDB 生成的 _id。
# @name demoCreate
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Demo User",
  "email": "demo-user-{{$timestamp}}@example.com",
  "age": 28,
  "addresses": [
    {
      "recipient": "Demo User",
      "phone": "13800000000",
      "province": "Shanghai",
      "city": "Shanghai",
      "detailAddress": "Demo Road 1"
    }
  ]
}

### 3. List users - 创建后,确认新用户出现在列表里
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

### 4. Get user by id - 读取刚创建的用户
# Expected: 200,内容和上一步 Create 返回的一致。
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{demoCreate.response.body.$._id}}

### 5. Update user - 局部更新(只改 name/age,email/addresses 应保持不变)
# Expected: 200,返回更新后的对象。
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/{{demoCreate.response.body.$._id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Demo User (Updated)",
  "age": 35
}

### 6. Get user by id - 确认更新已持久化
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{demoCreate.response.body.$._id}}

### 7. Delete user - 删除
# Expected: 200 + 提示 message。
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/{{demoCreate.response.body.$._id}}

### 8. Get user by id - 确认已删除
# Expected: 404,证明删除真实生效,不是接口"假装成功"。
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{demoCreate.response.body.$._id}}


### ============================================================
### 二、边界与错误场景 · 400(格式 / 校验类)
### ============================================================

### Get user - invalid ObjectId format
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1

### Create user - missing email
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Missing Email User",
  "age": 20
}

### Create user - missing name
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "missing-name-{{$timestamp}}@example.com",
  "age": 20
}

### Create user - invalid email format
# Expected: 400,Model 的 `match` 校验拒绝非法邮箱格式。
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bad Email User",
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "age": 20
}

### Update user - invalid ObjectId format
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated User Name"
}

### Update user - empty body(没有任何可更新字段)
# Expected: 400 "No valid fields provided to update"。
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/{{missingUserId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Delete user - invalid ObjectId format
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/1


### ============================================================
### 三、边界与错误场景 · 404(格式合法但资源不存在)
### ============================================================

### Get user - valid format, no matching user
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{missingUserId}}

### Update user - valid format, no matching user
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/{{missingUserId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ghost User"
}

### Delete user - valid format, no matching user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/{{missingUserId}}


### ============================================================
### 四、边界与错误场景 · 409(email 唯一性冲突)
### 注意:这组内部有顺序依赖,要从上到下按顺序整组跑(seed A/B → 两条 409 → 两条清理),
### 不能像上面 400/404 那样挑单条点。
### ============================================================

### Create seed user A - 占用一个邮箱,给下面两条 409 用
# @name seedUserA
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Seed User A",
  "email": "seed-a-{{$timestamp}}@example.com",
  "age": 30
}

### Create seed user B - 用来测试"改成别人的邮箱"这条路径
# @name seedUserB
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Seed User B",
  "email": "seed-b-{{$timestamp}}@example.com",
  "age": 31
}

### Create user - duplicate email(和 Seed User A 撞邮箱)
# Expected: 409。
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Duplicate Email Attempt",
  "email": "{{seedUserA.response.body.$.email}}",
  "age": 32
}

### Update user - duplicate email(把 Seed User B 的邮箱改成 Seed User A 的)
# Expected: 409。
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/{{seedUserB.response.body.$._id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{seedUserA.response.body.$.email}}"
}

### 清理:删除 Seed User A,不留 demo 垃圾数据
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/{{seedUserA.response.body.$._id}}

### 清理:删除 Seed User B,不留 demo 垃圾数据
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/{{seedUserB.response.body.$._id}}
</content>
